{"tid":2499325,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美華裔夫婦盜取醫院機密帶返中國 分別囚30、33個月","createTime":"2021-04-21T21:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T22:14:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bcaa3b8cdf0bdd83bfe05ccca4bf1f83dec60708","tid":2499325,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T21:55:28.000Z","msg":"法庭文件顯示，兩名被告分別為51歲的周宇（Yu Zhou）和47歲的陳莉（Li Chen）， 二人在俄亥俄州國家兒童醫院實驗室擔任研究員。他們被控在實驗室任職的十年間，竊取至少五項有關利用胞外體（exosomke）來治療癌症的商業秘密，並且從中國政府、中國國家外國專家局和中國國家自然科學基金會等地方獲取利益。2015年，他們在中國秘密成立一家胞外體公司，製造和販賣相關產品，2016年更於中國獲得與被盜技術有關的專利。<br />\n<br />\n事件被揭發後，二人認罪。陳莉早於今年2月於被判囚33個月，周宇則於周一（4月19日）被判囚33個月。除服刑外，二人也被沒收約值145萬元（美元、下同，約1,125萬港元）的股票，以及賠償260萬元（約2,000萬港元）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210422/FVTZNEQSMFHIFHIKJ2F62DMVYA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210422%2FFVTZNEQSMFHIFHIKJ2F62DMVYA%2F&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5Clnb4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=f81835b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210422%2FFVTZNEQSMFHIFHIKJ2F62DMVYA%2F&h=02ddf0b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210422/FVTZNEQSMFHIFHIKJ2F62DMVYA/</a>"},{"pid":"e8d569b107bd78f2779583e3c04558aa4af606a6","tid":2499325,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPvBBswErTXUPNdnd6Fy4d2S4FCRhLSJ4hfUSoS6L9e1k?filename=K6kqApW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6kqApW.jpg&h=44f75a97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4391e4a1bce5382c4faeb0809920befa965ed969","tid":2499325,"uid":65289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:14:48.000Z","msg":"便宜左佢<br />\no係美國坐"}]}